                        </persName> held of him in <placeName key="place_103133">Cugric</placeName> and 
                  <placeName type="minor">Ploxlandes</placeName> and <placeName key="place_103148">Ecoppe</placeName>, and <placeName key="place_103046">Adel</placeName>; paying 8s. yearly.
                     (<origDate notBefore="1150" notAfter="1160" precision="low">c. 1150-60</origDate>)
